40 std::vector<uint8_t> uncompress(std::vector<uint8_t> const &data)
41 {
42  uLong comp_size = data.size()-sizeof(CompressedPacketHeader);
43  const CompressedPacket *compressed_packet = reinterpret_cast<const CompressedPacket*>(data.data());

45  std::vector<uint8_t> ret(decomp_size);

47  if(decomp_ret != Z_OK)
48  {
49  std::cerr << "uncompress: comp size: " << comp_size << std::endl;
50  std::cerr << "uncompress: decomp size in: " << compressed_packet->uncompressed_size << std::endl;
51  std::cerr << "uncompress: decomp size out: " << decomp_size << std::endl;
52  switch(decomp_ret)
53  {
54  case Z_MEM_ERROR:
55  std::cerr << "uncompress: not enough memory" << std::endl;
56  break;

61  std::cerr << "uncompress: corrupt or incomplete input data" << std::endl;
